at culture (India), and that Americans have no culture. Not so. She has been living in it for so long that she is a fish in the American cultural ocean – it&amp;rsquo;s invisible. People leave the world in droves to come to America, for the culture. The culture of freedom, individual liberty, open-ness, and protection from the greatest slaughterer of mankind, government. I&amp;rsquo;ll take that any day over colorful clothing and spicy food.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
